{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2349884, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "社会阶级也变为经济主导，姓氏不再体现任何阶级信息", "timestamp": 1629833104, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349885, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本身没有意义，但当对方说“必须”的时候就有意义了", "timestamp": 1629833133, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349886, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "请dz改名", "timestamp": 1629833151, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349887, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": 2349885, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 看见很多女生都是这样想的，dz也认同。但dz更认同取消姓氏这个矛盾源，它没有任何意义还激化性别矛盾", "timestamp": 1629833230, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349888, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": 2349886, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我不敢，我爸妈要揍我", "timestamp": 1629833258, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349889, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": 2349886, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但我很期待取消姓氏的那天", "timestamp": 1629833299, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349890, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "第一曾爷爷的名字还是叫得上的；第二看全红婵入族谱就知道“宗族意识淡漠”有很多限定条件", "timestamp": 1629833365, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349891, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": 2349890, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 那你很厉害，dz连“老家”都没回过，别提族谱了", "timestamp": 1629833417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349892, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": 2349890, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 那曾姥姥的名字叫得上吗？她和你曾爷爷从血缘上一样亲", "timestamp": 1629833478, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349893, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没什么意义但是去掉会觉得很怪", "timestamp": 1629833692, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349894, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz觉得姓氏、冠姓权跟传统宗族观念关系不大了，只作为一个习惯而传承", "timestamp": 1629833786, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349925, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": 2349891, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果真的能取消也挺好的\n不管是取消，抽签，任选还是其他天马行空的算法，都不错", "timestamp": 1629837759, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349930, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": 2349888, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果姓氏这么无所谓，你改名爸妈为什么要揍你？再推一步，如果你的孩子不跟你姓，你觉得爸妈会有意见吗？\n很多“传统”现在只是看上去式微，但潜移默化的力量是很强大的\n何况宗族意识淡漠并不适用于所有地区和人，仍然存在许多宗族关系非常强势的地方，这种时候姓氏传承真的是重男轻女的来源之一", "timestamp": 1629839448, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我感觉Eve说得对。但对真正宗族意识淡漠的个体（比如dz，以及cz也是）来说却是不太无所谓，我们的下一代（如果有的话）改名大概不会被我们揍hhh", "timestamp": 1629843554, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2349965, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "2333，我清晰知道我外婆的姓名，大致记得外公的姓名，爷爷奶奶全都不记得", "timestamp": 1629845826, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2350001, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 449476, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "日本结婚还要随夫姓呢，提了20年不随夫姓的option现在都还没能通过。要说生活中的影响确实没多少影响，但是它确实潜移默化形成了依附男性的身份认同。", "timestamp": 1629850262, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 449476, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "看sd震撼我，想问问姓氏有什么用吗？在宗族意识淡漠至此的今天（你曾爷爷叫啥你都说不上来），它的存在有任何意义吗", "timestamp": 1629833056, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629856346, "url": "", "vote": {}}}